@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #ECEFF1
skinparam classBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam classBorderColor #455A64
skinparam shadowing true
[*] --> Rejected
Rejected --> Reviewed : reject
Reviewed --> Processing : reject
Reviewed : entry / log medicalrecord
Processing --> Closed : cancel
Closed --> Archived : review
Closed : entry / log medicalrecord
Archived --> [*]
@enduml